{"id": 3023, "genre": 1000, "title": "有了网络之后，哪些“数字劳动”你已经习以为常了？", "description": "哪些事情会让你觉得，线上生活乍看轻松愉快，但其实却是一种隐藏的“劳作”？（题图来自：iStock ©️ jossnatu）", "record_count": 6455, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20191007215835ebnxa45KwlENgyVW.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-10-07T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 5959, "title": "有了网络之后，哪些“数字劳动”你已经习以为常了？", "content": "现如今，哪些新型“数字劳动”你已经习以为常了？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 347951, "content": "为了线上信息不被泄露，花时间做的各种安全措施", "image": "img/option/option/20191007203454m9WFjvpc1tnOqSVh.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 347954, "content": "为了不被垃圾信息打扰，要自己设置层层屏蔽功能", "image": "img/option/option/20191007204629vdiLpqRZ0ganHxtY.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 347955, "content": "在广告/垃圾资讯里寻找有用资料，花掉的大量时间", "image": "img/option/option/20191007205409i9JRGYP8zxe3mfnt.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 347956, "content": "有了移动办公后，工作和生活间越来越模糊的界限", "image": "img/option/option/20191007205755S16GCMakOQ9fBKL4.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 347957, "content": "信息过载带来的情绪劳动，比如压力、焦虑和无聊", "image": "img/option/option/20191007210738a5th4mjCDn0WKbUx.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 347959, "content": "应付线上社交中的各种（比线下更复杂的）social 规则", "image": "img/option/option/20191007212020GLP1CJ5VspHYkTDu.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 347960, "content": "防杠精/防线上沟通的各色（在线下本可避免的）冲突", "image": "img/option/option/20191007212747SzGubcdl7qZVf8m4.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 347961, "content": "防止流行语/热点对注意力的透支，抵抗娱乐过载疲劳", "image": "img/option/option/201910072143146A5zfHWNqLcJymh7.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}